# Root .gitignore for ERP System (Backend and FrontEnd)

## Build and Output Directories
Backend/**/bin/
Backend/**/obj/
FrontEnd/dist/
FrontEnd/tmp/
FrontEnd/out-tsc/
FrontEnd/bazel-out/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/

## IDE and Editor files
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates

## Dependency Directories
FrontEnd/node_modules/
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log

## Caches and temporary files
FrontEnd/.angular/
.angular/
.sass-cache/
.history/
coverage/
testem.log
/libpeerconnection.log

## System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
